---
title: Mexican Smashed Bean & Beef Rice Bowl with Cucumber Salsa & Pickled Onion
description: Say hello to the king of beef and veggie bowls! There's nutrient-packed cannellini that are wholesome and filling, garlic rice and cucumber salsa, plus a sublime helping of cheesy goodness and a sprinkling of toasted pumpkin seeds for extra crunch. Enjoy!

*We’ve replaced the chickpeas in this recipe with cannellini beans due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
